name: DaleCarnegiePrinciples
0:
”Alexa, open Dale Carnegie Principles”
”Alexa, start Dale Carnegie Principles”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dale carnegie principles
des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of Dale Carnegie's principles from How To Win Friends and Influence People and How To Stop Worrying and Start Living. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next principle. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
